title: Changeling Encounter: Leah
description: In this day of inflated gas prices and living expenses, don't you think it's time you got something back? How about a fantasy meeting in an abandoned room or a brief encounter in a Mercedes-Benz? How about a trip into the exotic with the lover that sets your passions ablaze? You earned it! You deserve it. And we're going to give it to you!
author: Jessica Coulter Smith
